PLEASE NOTICE the paths, its might not works on other computers, YOU MUST CHANGE manually all paths depending the new location given when cloning this repo.

Open file mode
 Value | Description
-------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 r     | Read mode, if file does not exist, raises an IOError exception.
-------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 w     | Write mode, creates file if it doesn’t exist, otherwise overwrites it.
-------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 a     | Append mode, adds data to the end of the file.
-------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 b     | Binary mode, used for handling binary data (like images or complex structures).
-------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 r+    | Read and write mode, raises an IOError if the file does not exist.
-------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 w+    | Write and read mode, creates the file if it doesn’t exist, overwrites otherwise.
-------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 a+    | Append and read mode, creates file if it doesn’t exist.
-------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 rb    | Read binary mode, opens a binary file for reading.
-------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 wb    | Write binary mode, opens a binary file for writing, creates it if it doesn’t exist.
-------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 ab    | Append binary mode, opens a binary file for appending.
-------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 rb+   | Read and write binary mode.
-------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 wb+   | Write and read binary mode, creates file if it doesn’t exist, overwrites otherwise.
-------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 ab+   | Append and read binary mode, creates the file if it doesn’t exist.
-------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

